NYT-10-20-98 1512EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19981020.0144 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-20 15:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7044 &Cx1f; tad-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JOURNAL-ITALY-$ADV22-     10-20 0785
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JOURNAL-ITALY-$ADV22-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    JOURNAL: WHAT COUNTRY IS THIS, ANYWAY?
 &HT;    With photo mug of Holmes placed in the International folder on
the Cox Server.
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (k) Commentary
categories.
 &HT;    For Use Thursday, Oct. 22 And Thereafter.
 &HT;    By CHARLES W. HOLMES 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
