<P>
   UNDATED _ Maybe, like one addict, you believe your $400 phone
bill must be paid before the $40 water bill. Maybe you don't have
time for the people you love but who just seem to take so much
effort, and you'd rather connect with new friends on the Net. Or
maybe it's simpler. Maybe you just find your fingers anxiously
making typing movements when you're away from your computer. If any
of this is true, it may be that you're addicted to the Internet. By
CAROLYN POIROT. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
