   MIDEAST-TALKS (Washington) _ King Hussein of Jordan throws his
considerable prestige into the Middle East peace talks as he joins
President Clinton to push for an accord between Israeli Prime
Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat.
By NANCY MATHIS. (Already filed.)
</P>
