   MIDEAST-PALESTINIANS (Hebron, West Bank) _ Salem Rajab Sarsour,
the Palestinian man who reportedly confessed to Monday's grenade
attack at a crowded bus stop, is a double agent who works for the
terrorist group Hamas and the Israeli government, Palestinian
authorities and Israeli television say. By DEBORAH HORAN. (Already
filed.)
