in the gubernatorial election scheduled Sunday in the northeastern
state of Tamaulipas. The official accuses the ruling Institutional
Revolutionary Party of using state resources to help the campaign
of Tomas Yarrington Ruvalcaba. By PHILIP TRUE. (Already filed.)
