<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: THIS STORY IS MOVING ON FINANCIAL AND NATIONAL WIRES 
 
WATCH THE WEB TO KEEP UP WITH THE TWISTS AND TURNS IN THE MICROSOFT
TRIAL 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  By DWIGHT SILVERMAN 
c.1998 Houston Chronicle 
 
